<br>
Incorrect.<br>
<br>
1989, PCH, Santa Maria, Ca., northern end of VAFB.  Single vehicle accident, Ford Taurus 2dr sedan, vaulted over guard rail, right side - no seat belts worn, driver BAC less than .03.  Coroner's report indicates high THC level in both victims.  Passenger died in transit, driver presumed dead on scene.  Investigation reveals driver apparently lost control of vehicle due to THC-induced impaired judgement and loss of motor skills.  <br>
<br>
<br>
Fact - THC (the 'drug' in pot) impairs your motor skills, increases your reaction times, alters your perception of events around you, and has detrimental effects on your short term memory (shown by research).  <br>
<br>
<br>
It's not a moral argument - the research bears out the fact that pot does have an adverse affect on drivers.  Much like alcohol.  <br>
<br>
If you want to legalize pot, fine.  Write your congressman and lobby the system.  Regulate pot like we currently regulate alcohol.  But spouting statements like that in the face of evidence is stupid.  You don't help your position any.  <br>
<br>
You wanna smoke up?  Fine.  Stay the @#%$ off the roads, get a taxi, smoke up in your own house.  I don't care.  But don't drive.  Not that hard.  <br>
<br>
<br>
As for the guy who died and his chat friends?  <br>
<br>
Anyone who will ingest anything harmful to prove how 'hardcore' that person is to his/her peers has some serious psychological issues.   <br>
<br>
As for his 'friends'.....  well, hope they relive that moment for the rest of their lives.   <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.mojohurricane.com/images/eqstuff/profiles/pafsmile3.jpg" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:yellow;font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Dr. Pafuna, PhD</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></span><!--EZCODE FONT END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:yellow;font-family:verdana;font-size:xx-small;"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Defiler, Mad Scientist, Gran Sous BBQ Chef</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></span><!--EZCODE FONT END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:yellow;font-family:verdana;font-size:xx-small;">Morell Thule Grammar Nazi</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--></strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=533476" target="blank"><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:yellow;font-family:verdana;font-size:xx-small;"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Twitch-Witch Toolbox</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></span><!--EZCODE FONT END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub169.ezboard.com/bmtboards.showUserPublicProfile?gid=pafuna>Pafuna</A> at: 2/5/03 12:42:54 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#102960><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub169.ezboard.com/bmtboards.showUserPublicProfile?gid=cannabulon>Cannabulon</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="htt