This is a tricky thing Paf, you see &quot;High THC level&quot; means nothing more than they were heavy pot smokers. Marijuanna doesnt metabolize out of the system for 30 days or more sometimes, so the problem with the argument of &quot;They were high&quot; is that they could have been high 3 hours, 8 hours, or 10 days ago.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>Fact - THC (the 'drug' in pot) impairs your motor skills, increases your reaction times, alters your perception of events around you, and has detrimental effects on your short term memory (shown by research). <br>
