<br>
I agree with the first three, however the short term memory thing, that is only WHILE high, there is NO research showing long term memory impairment or damage to memory. If you have it by all means let me know which medical journal that appeared in, or quote the study with paranthetical documentation because I wont believe that till I see it.<br>
