<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>Data has shown that while smoking marijuana, people show the same lack of coordination on standard &quot;drunk driver&quot; tests as do people who have had too much to drink<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
