Just a few years ago here in Ottawa, a tractor trailer driver, high on marijuana (as confirmed by the presence of THC in his bloodstream, and warm joint stubs in his ash tray), jumped the curb off the main highway through town and drove his truck down into the bus tunnel, crushing to death 2 women and one of the two babies they were walking with.<br>
